 is impossible to introduce backdoors for third parties or to hide vulnerabilities, so you do not need to trust Cryptomator. Also, vendor lock-ins are impossible. Even if we decided to stop development: The source code is already cloned by hundreds of other developers and development can be picked up by othersgversionf1.17.0ldownload_urlxghttps://github.com/cryptomator/cryptomator/releases/download/1.17.0/cryptomator-1.17.0-aarch64.AppImagedsizeh53.03 MBhsrc_urlsüx3https://github.com/cryptomator/cryptomator/releaseshweb_urlsüxhttps://github.com/cryptomatorhprovideskcryptomatorglicenseüpGPL-3.0-or-laterkmaintainersx9AppImage (https://github.com/AppImage/appimage.github.io)enotesćx:[EXTERNAL] (This is an unofficial, third-party repository)xI[UNTRUSTED] (We CAN NOT guarantee the authenticity, validity or security)x2This data was autogenerated & is likely inaccuratex/Data used: https://appimage.github.io/feed.jsonx;Provided by: https://github.com/AppImage/appimage.github.ioxNLearn More: https://docs.pkgforge.dev/repositories/external/appimage.github.iox;Please create an Issue or send a PR for an official Package«cpkgodbgate.appimagehpkg_namefdbgatefpkg_idx appimage.github.io.DbGate.dbgatediconx~https://raw.githubusercontent.com/AppImage/appimage.github.io/refs/heads/master/database/icons/DbGate/icons/256x256/dbgate.pngkdescriptionx'Opensource database administration toolgversionfv6.5.4ldownload_urlxVhttps://github.com/dbgate/dbgate/releases/download/v6.5.4/dbgate-latest-arm64.AppImagedsizei151.97 MBhsrc_urlsüx)https://github.com/dbgate/dbgate/releaseshweb_urlsüxhttps://github.com/dbgatehprovidesfdbgateglicenseücMITkmaintainersx9AppImage (https://github.com/AppImage/appimage.github.io)enotesćx:[EXTERNAL] (This is an unofficial, third-party repository)xI[UNTRUSTED] (We CAN NOT guarantee the authenticity, validity or security)x2This data was autogenerated & is likely inaccuratex/Data used: https://appimage.github.io/feed.jsonx;Provided by: https://github.com/AppImage/app