st your build, you can do so. Eternal Lands is not just about combat. Many players focus on more peaceful activities such as collecting resources, creating items, summoning monsters and so on. But if you like combat, there is plenty of it as well, both PvP and PvE. Eternal Lands is owned and run by Radu Privantu. This package is built and maintained by one of the client developers known in game as bluapgversioni1.9.7.0-4ldownload_urlxphttps://github.com/raduprv/Eternal-Lands/releases/download/1.9.7.0-4/EternalLands-Linux-aarch64_1.9.7.0.AppImagedsizei209.46 MBhsrc_urlsüx1https://github.com/raduprv/Eternal-Lands/releaseshweb_urlsüxhttps://github.com/raduprvhprovidesmeternal-landsglicenseügQPL-1.0kmaintainersx9AppImage (https://github.com/AppImage/appimage.github.io)enotesćx:[EXTERNAL] (This is an unofficial, third-party repository)xI[UNTRUSTED] (We CAN NOT guarantee the authenticity, validity or security)x2This data was autogenerated & is likely inaccuratex/Data used: https://appimage.github.io/feed.jsonx;Provided by: https://github.com/AppImage/appimage.github.ioxNLearn More: https://docs.pkgforge.dev/repositories/external/appimage.github.iox;Please create an Issue or send a PR for an official Package«cpkgrexplorook.appimagehpkg_nameiexplorookfpkg_idx$appimage.github.io.Explorook.Rookoutdiconxähttps://raw.githubusercontent.com/AppImage/appimage.github.io/refs/heads/master/database/icons/Explorook/icons/128x128/explorook.pngkdescriptionx9RookoutŌĆÖs site addon to support local files and foldersgversiongv1.16.6ldownload_urlxhhttps://github.com/Rookout/explorook/releases/download/v1.16.6/Rookout-Desktop-App-1.16.6-arm64.AppImagedsizei103.41 MBhsrc_urlsüx-https://github.com/Rookout/explorook/releaseshweb_urlsüxhttps://github.com/RookouthprovidesiexplorookglicenseüjApache-2.0kmaintainersx9AppImage (https://github.com/AppImage/appimage.github.io)enotesćx:[EXTERNAL] (This is an unofficial, third-party repository)xI[UNTRUSTED] (We CAN NOT guarantee the authenticity, valid