eering, architecture and 3D printing. FreeCAD allows you to sketch geometry constrained 2D shapes and use them as a base to build other objects. It contains many components to adjust dimensions or extract design details from 3D models to create high quality production-ready drawings. it is a multiplatfom (Windows, Mac and Linux), highly customizable using the Python language. It reads and writes to many open file formats such as STEP, IGES, STL, SVG, DXF, OBJ, IFC, DAE and many others, making it possible to seamlessly integrate it into your workflow. FreeCAD includes a modern Finite Element Analysis (FEA) tools, experimental CFD, BIM, Geodata workbenches, a Path (CNC) workbench, a robot simulation module that allows you to study robot movements and many more, and a rich collection of plugins and macros installable directly from within the applicationgversionn20240407stableldownload_urlxéhttps://github.com/realthunder/FreeCAD/releases/download/20240407stable/FreeCAD-Link-Stable-Linux-aarch64-py3.11-20240407.AppImagedsizei819.31 MBhsrc_urlsüx/https://github.com/realthunder/FreeCAD/releaseshweb_urlsüxhttps://github.com/realthunderhprovideslfreecad-asm3glicenseühLGPL-2.1kmaintainersx9AppImage (https://github.com/AppImage/appimage.github.io)enotesćx:[EXTERNAL] (This is an unofficial, third-party repository)xI[UNTRUSTED] (We CAN NOT guarantee the authenticity, validity or security)x2This data was autogenerated & is likely inaccuratex/Data used: https://appimage.github.io/feed.jsonx;Provided by: https://github.com/AppImage/appimage.github.ioxNLearn More: https://docs.pkgforge.dev/repositories/external/appimage.github.iox;Please create an Issue or send a PR for an official Package«cpkgqfreecad2.appimagehpkg_namehfreecad2fpkg_idx#appimage.github.io.FreeCAD2.FreeCADdiconxģhttps://raw.githubusercontent.com/AppImage/appimage.github.io/refs/heads/master/database/icons/FreeCAD2/icons/64x64/freecad_conda.pngkdescriptionyĆFreeCAD is a parametric 3D modeler. Parametric modeling al